{"tid":733962,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一件俾龜截趣事","createTime":"2018-07-08T08:30:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-09T00:50:41.000Z","uid":3912,"like":7,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0dd798d80ac81f5979e54be66530525de518cada","tid":733962,"uid":3912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T08:30:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n諗起之前fb有單係個好人摸㗎波子頭話副計凍㗎喎應該泊咗好耐啦又係好好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02e1636f87f3b7c269e29dd6080c5d2c328dd556","tid":733962,"uid":52068,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T10:59:10.000Z","msg":"藍牙同緊個frd講電話<br />\n點知入路障嗰時，個仆街frd笑住咁講話：啊蛇，依條友車尾箱有粉<br />\n我同個猶差你眼望我眼，最後乜事都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa900cf6a9c31bff22f41d768e04c63870505425","tid":733962,"uid":140834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T11:33:03.000Z","msg":"初初揸車入錯屋邨巴士通道，入後波出番屋邨大路，<br />\n撞正慈母做完大搞作收爐，心諗金翅hihi鳥。<br />\n唯有向慈母坦白講我想去既地點，然後問我見唔見到頭先都截左架車，<br />\n我搭無因為我乜都唔知淨係諗住入波走，<br />\n最後佢放過一馬。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bbeae299bc3e3ef03533df730fb5f89c84f9531","tid":733962,"uid":28418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T00:50:41.000Z","msg":"用國際牌入左超速block 佢話寄到俾你就寄<br />\n寄唔到就你好彩<br />\n真係冇寄黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實香港身分證都唔得國際牌 但過左兩次骨"}]}